<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="trick-vt">trick <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /trɪk/    美 /trɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>欺骗；哄骗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d been tricked and I felt stupid. 
我被骗了，觉得自己真傻。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>An advertiser might be trying to <strong>trick</strong> customers <strong>into</strong> buying a product or a service.
广告商可能试图哄骗顾客购买产品或服务。</p></div></div>